overview: In 2006 Faithless released their fifth studio album "To All New Arrivals" Successive world tours have enshrined their popularity all over the globe and this is clearly evident as they delight their Moscow fans as part of this Greatest Hits Tour. Traklist 1 	Sweep  2 	Insomnia  3 	Emergency  4 	All Races And Colours  5 	God Is A DJ  6 	Bring My Family Back  7 	Mass Destruction  8 	Everything Will Be Alright Tomorrow  9 	What About Love  10 	Bombs  11 	Drifting Away  12 	Music Matters  13 	Miss U Less, Miss U More  14 	I Want More  15 	We Come 1  16 	Muhammad Ali  17 	Salva Mea
